titles.title: For the relief of Dylan Brian Benwell.

action.text: Referred to the House Committee on the Judiciary.
Referred to the Subcommittee on Immigration, Border Security, and Claims.

bill.summary: 10/5/2004--Introduced. Considers Dylan Brian Benwell to be a naturalized citizen of the United States and shall be furnished by the Secretary of Homeland Security with a certificate of such naturalization.
